author_ssm: Jenny Pachucki, 2007. Finding aid completed by Luke Martin and Christine Woody, 2009.
abstract_ssm: The Terence Sellers Papers include materials that relate to the art and literary scene in New York City in the 1970s and 1980s. The collection includes Sellers' writing, journals, photographs, and materials relating to her career as a professional writer.
